{"tid":164289,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[我問你答] 點解果次老豆發作挑撥離間","createTime":"2017-03-20T14:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T01:42:28.000Z","uid":79353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f58859e43071013c067321750bcf5ffb489c8213","tid":164289,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"話說我老豆呢個人一向十分極度正常及顧家<br />\n<br />\n件事是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我地屋企由若干年前開始，用我個名捐錢俾慈善機構<br />\n<br />\n但只不過係用我個名，D錢實則上係由阿媽銀行戶口自動轉賬<br />\n<br />\n由於我已經返左工一段時間有少少收入<br />\n<br />\n所以果次我就想用返自己銀行轉口轉錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/6790bbb9eca33e1f972d0fd9552aae32.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F6790bbb9eca33e1f972d0fd9552aae32.gif&h=3977ae48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對話內容如下:<br />\n<br />\n我: 不如捐錢果度我自己俾返錢~ 用返我銀行戶口俾錢~ (差唔多意思，非原文)<br />\n<br />\n爸: 阿姐呢（ME）而家就想同媽媽劃清界線......<br />\n<br />\n(太長的對話唔記得左，不過成段話都係佢無啦啦發癲挑撥離間，之後我地成家靜晒，家母臉有難色，講真我真係唔知老豆做乜，佢無啦啦發癲，明明平時好正常)<br />\n<br />\n-分隔線--<br />\n<br />\n所以你地話我老豆做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3742e6e44e92d509c76e71be2834e3eec9e873","tid":164289,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"阿姐做咩呀又"},{"pid":"7ebe122e092de4af29f07f027b781b2f0640a253","tid":164289,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿姐做咩呀又</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b247bc5a6e0da33eae97098f8145597a6ed61034","tid":164289,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿姐做咩呀又</blockquote><br />\n我以後叫你阿羊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e483acd6c931cbfc27945026f28ee9f97f9fa1","tid":164289,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:28:01.000Z"